      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">If you play Scrabble internationally, SOWPODS gives you access to roughly 40,000 extra words that North American players cannot use. Knowing these SOWPODS-exclusive words can be a decisive advantage in international competition, online play, and casual games that adopt the Collins dictionary.</p>

