      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Strategy for International Play</h2>
      <p>When transitioning from TWL to SOWPODS play, focus first on the additional two-letter words — they unlock the most board positions. Then learn high-scoring short words with J, Q, X, and Z that don't appear in TWL.</p>

