      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Know Your Dictionary Before You Play</h2>
      <p>The single most important rule: always confirm which dictionary your game uses before the first tile is placed. Online platforms typically default to one dictionary — most international platforms use SOWPODS, and NASPA-sanctioned games use TWL.</p>

